---
title: SuperQuick Honey-Dijon Tilapia  with Grape-and-Goat Cheese Salad
description: Zippy honey-mustard sauce pulls double duty in this dinner, as a glaze for pan-fried tilapia and as the base for a tangy salad dressing! Plus, pops of grape combine with creamy goat cheese to pack flavour and texture into the perfect side salad for this meal.

